# Implementation guides (for agents)

Current-state reference for working in this codebase. Add guides when a subsystem is non-trivial.

**When to use:** You have an issue and need patterns, file locations, and guardrails.

**When not to use:** Picking work or release process. Use [orchestration.md](../orchestration.md) and [docs/ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md).

